         <h2 class="listing-title blog"> <a href="/blog/earthscope-national-meeting-2015" title="EarthScope National Meeting 2015" rel="bookmark">EarthScope National Meeting 2015</a> </h2> 
         <div>
          <span>By</span> Sarah Robinson | 
          <i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i> 
          <time class="entry-date" datetime="2015-02-16T14:44:00-07:00">February 16th, 2015 at 02:44PM MST</time>
         </div> 
        </header> 
        <div class="feature-image center"> 
         <a href="/blog/earthscope-national-meeting-2015" title="EarthScope National Meeting 2015" rel="bookmark"> <img src="/images/made/9d33bdf848b305de/stowe-vermont-no-copyright-patrick-from-barrington-ri-moretown-vt-united-states_640_402.jpg" alt="EarthScope National Meeting 2015" width="640" height="402"> </a> 
         <div class="caption center">
           Photo of Stowe, Vermont. Photo credit "The World Through Photos". 
         </div> 
        </div> 
        <div class="entry-summary"> 
         <p>The EarthScope National Meeting will be held in Stowe, Vermont June 15-17, 2015. More information will be made available soon at the <a href="http://www.earthscope.org/events/2015-earthscope-national-meeting">2015 EarthScope National Meeting</a> page.</p> 
