        <header class="entry-header"> 
         <h2 class="listing-title blog"> <a href="/blog/2015-earthscope-national-meeting" title="2015 EarthScope National Meeting" rel="bookmark">2015 EarthScope National Meeting</a> </h2> 
         <div>
          <span>By</span> Sarah Robinson | 
          <i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i> 
          <time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-07-21T10:38:00-06:00">July 21st, 2014 at 10:38AM MDT</time>
         </div> 
        </header> 
        <div class="feature-image center"> 
         <a href="/blog/2015-earthscope-national-meeting" title="2015 EarthScope National Meeting" rel="bookmark"> <img src="/images/made/9d33bdf848b305de/ES_Logo_Blue_640_480.jpg" alt="2015 EarthScope National Meeting" width="640" height="480"> </a> 
         <div class="caption center"></div> 
        </div> 
        <div class="entry-summary"> 
         <p>Save the dates of June 14-17, 2015 for the biennial EarthScope National Meeting.&nbsp; The meeting will be in Stowe, Vermont.<br> &nbsp;<br> Conference highlights include the opportunity to showcase your research in the poster sessions, hear firsthand results of pioneering EarthScope studies, contribute to the discussion on the future after EarthScope, and participate in a field trip (tentative) with local EarthScope scientists.</p> 
         <p>More information coming soon.&nbsp;</p> 
        </div> 
