         <h2 class="listing-title blog"> <a href="/blog/earthscope-scientist-find-evidence-for-deep-water" title="EarthScope Scientists Find Evidence for “Deep Water”" rel="bookmark">EarthScope Scientists Find Evidence for “Deep Water”</a> </h2> 
         <div>
          <span>By</span> Sarah Robinson | 
          <i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i> 
          <time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-06-16T15:37:00-06:00">June 16th, 2014 at 03:37PM MDT</time>
         </div> 
        </header> 
        <div class="feature-image center"> 
         <a href="/blog/earthscope-scientist-find-evidence-for-deep-water" title="EarthScope Scientists Find Evidence for “Deep Water”" rel="bookmark"> <img src="/images/made/9d33bdf848b305de/earthscope-globe-instruments_500_513.jpg" alt="EarthScope Scientists Find Evidence for “Deep Water”" width="500" height="513"> </a> 
         <div class="caption center"></div> 
        </div> 
        <div class="entry-summary"> 
         <p>New findings from EarthScope researchers at Northwestern University and the University of New Mexico show evidence for "potentially oceans worth of deep water beneath the United States".</p> 
